1
00:00:04,900 --> 00:00:08,000
<v sp1>（</v> <v sp1>和平</v> <v sp1>）</v> <v sp1>ただーいま</v> <v sp1>。</v>
<v sp1>あれ？</v>  <v sp1>先輩</v> <v sp1>。</v>

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:09,666
